divs: Sighting DetailsI was at the intersection of Rt 20 and Rt. 104 in Princeton, while my Mom was shopping. Playing around with my video camera, I thought I spied a gleaming white ufo hovering in a cloud bank. Not too sure. This camera, though New is pretty small. I'm going to try to attach the video to this and let you be the judge. If I was mistaken, I do apologize. This little section of West Virginia seems to be a hotbed of activity. I've spied 1 gleaming white sombrero typed craft. 3 black triangulars. And 1 gleaming white diamond shaped craft. Someone should come down here around Rt 104 near the Princeton Church of God to check it out.
